sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 👤 User
    actor Creator as 🤖 Creator Claude
    participant WS as 🐍 ws.py
    participant FS as 📂 Filesystem
    participant Tmux as 🪟 tmux
    participant Bend as 🏗️ bend serve
    participant HSC as 🧰 hsclaude
    actor WsC as 🤖 Workspace Claude
    participant MCP as 🔌 devex-mcp-server

    Note over User,Creator: /ws up ws-test customer-data-table
    User->>Creator: spin up a workspace
    Creator->>WS: plan <name> <repos>
    WS->>FS: read ~/src/<repo>, discovery cache
    FS-->>WS: remote URLs, cache hits
    WS-->>Creator: plan JSON (ok, repos, branches)
    Creator->>User: confirmation plan
    User->>Creator: yes

    Creator->>FS: Write /tmp/ws-<name>-init-prompt.txt
    Creator->>WS: init <name> --repos repo:branch

    rect rgb(255, 243, 205)
        Note over WS,Bend: Setup phase — blocks ~2–4 min
        WS->>FS: mkdir workspaces/<name>/
        par clone + yarn in parallel
            WS->>FS: git clone <repo>
            WS->>FS: bend yarn
        end
        WS->>FS: discover packages, update discovery cache
        WS->>Bend: Popen(bend reactor serve ..., start_new_session=True)
        WS->>FS: write <ws_dir>/.ws-serve.json (pid, lstart, marker, pkgPaths)
        Bend->>FS: write route-configs/<pid>-introspection
        loop ≤ 120s until fresh introspection appears
            WS->>FS: stat route-configs/*
        end
        Note right of WS: bend is registered — safe to spawn the Workspace Claude
    end

    WS->>FS: write /tmp/ws-<name>-launch.sh
    WS->>Tmux: create workspace session, send-keys launcher
    Tmux->>HSC: hsclaude --name <name> "<handoff prompt>"
    HSC->>WsC: exec claude (with MCP config wired up)
    WsC->>MCP: spawn devex-mcp-server subprocess
    MCP->>FS: scan ~/.hubspot/route-configs/ at startup
    FS-->>MCP: <pid>-introspection (fresh)
    MCP-->>WsC: register bend_* as deferred tools
    WS-->>Creator: init JSON (tmuxSession, setup results)
    Creator->>User: "switch to tmux session <name>"

    Note over WsC: First action after handoff
    WsC->>WS: wait-ready <name>
    WsC->>WS: logs --grep "ERROR|FATAL|..."
    WsC->>WS: urls <name>
    WsC->>User: Workspace ready report (URLs, branches, log clean)

    Note over User,WsC: User works in the workspace
    User->>WsC: check the TS errors after this edit
    WsC->>WsC: ToolSearch query="bend" (load deferred tool schema)
    WsC->>MCP: bend_package_ts_get_errors(pkg)
    MCP->>Bend: query tools HTTP endpoint
    Bend-->>MCP: TS errors
    MCP-->>WsC: errors
    WsC->>User: report

    Note over User,WsC: Teardown
    User->>WsC: nuke this workspace
    WsC->>WS: nuke <name>
    WS->>FS: read <ws_dir>/.ws-serve.json → (pid, lstart)
    WS->>Bend: os.killpg(getpgid(pid), SIGTERM) then SIGKILL after 15s
    WS->>Tmux: kill workspace session
    WS->>FS: rm -rf workspaces/<name>/
    WS-->>WsC: done
    WsC->>User: workspace gone
